Gamescom 2014 is looming and Sony are bringing the fire. They have announced a press event (Tuesday, August 12 at 11am PT / 2pm ET / 7pm GMT – mark it in your calendar) and are bringing 52 games to their Gamescom booth. Of course, Sony would not be arranging a press event if they didn’t have something to show and judging by Sony’s Gamescom track record, we could be in for one hell of a weekend.
